---
title: Bacon Corn Chowder with Jalapeño and Homemade Garlic Bread
description: It's hard to beat a comforting warm bowl of chowder on a crisp cool day. Slightly smoked with Paprika and streaky bacon with garlic bread for dipping. Who needs to go out?!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-corn-chowder-de6c7f07.jpg
